{"tid":603987,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★有冇女科學主任？天文台開放日　氣象迷想同科學主任鑽研","createTime":"2018-03-24T09:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T09:23:49.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1b1a6a959001ff935a7eaa05d91b202e68a61ced","tid":603987,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T09:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/RX7p7QAKdzo/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FRX7p7QAKdzo%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=882082e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港天文台位於尖沙咀的總部，今日(24日)起一連兩日舉行一年一度的開放日，以今年世界氣象日的「智慧氣象」為主題設置展覽介紹天文台如何應用嶄新科技，包括天氣預報、航空氣象、微氣候監測及輻射監測等等。<br />\n<br />\n天文台今午12時起開放予公眾免費入場參觀，但未正式開放前已有近200名市民在場等候。鄒先生在10時已在總部門外排隊，笑言有多個有關颱風等問題想向科學主任請教。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180324/bkn-20180324140410409-0324_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180324%2Fbkn-20180324140410409-0324_00822_001.html&d=ZJyhSy%2F3CVi2leHjjJ8y7RFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=d588ec2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180324/bkn-20180324140410409-0324_00822_001.html</a>"}]}